title: I didnt get the 10 year celebration summoner icon
body: I got Riot Kayle, but i didnt get the 10 year celebration icon, i have played in the last couple of months so shouldnt i be able to get it?

replies.body:
*Zombiemaster* hit the nail right on the head. We've had to send these out in waves to ensure they get out properly.

Let me know if you don't have the icon by the 23rd.
The gifts are not done being distributed. The 23rd is the final day they will be given out, so if you don't receive it by then, you can submit a support ticket.
